title: The Havana Trendrome 7/20: Harvey Weinstein, Jungle Cruise, Linda Zeurn, Jackass Forever, Marjorie Taylor Greene, Havana Syndrome

description:
In this edition of The Havana Trendrome, Jack and Miles discuss Harvey Weinstein being extradited to California, Disney revamping their 'Jungle Cruise' ride without racist imagery, noted Trump supporter and antivaxxer Linda Zeurn dying of COVID-19, the new Jackass trailer, MTG being suspended from twitter temporarily, and a Havana Syndrome update
